8.3 
<emphasis box="[563,577,1404,1427]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">–</emphasis>
11.5 mm
</quantity>
(N=4).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="30.[151,1437,1004,1973]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
Head (fig. 96): Length 
<quantity box="[460,622,1439,1463]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.02" metricValueMax="1.11" metricValueMin="0.93" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" unit="mm" value="1.02" valueMax="1.11" valueMin="0.93">
0.93 
