</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="30.[151,1437,1004,1973]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
Thorax: Length 2.0 
<emphasis box="[429,443,1512,1535]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">–</emphasis>
<quantity box="[443,536,1511,1536]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.6" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" unit="mm" value="2.6">2.6 mm</quantity>
(N=4), width 2.0 mm (N=2). Dark brown, probably black in life. Haltere yellowish-brown.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="30.[151,1437,1004,1973]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
Wing (fig. 95): Length 
<quantity box="[462,597,1583,1608]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.0" metricValueMax="9.4" metricValueMin="8.6" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" unit="mm" value="9.0" valueMax="9.4" valueMin="8.6">
8.6 
<emphasis box="[497,511,1584,1607]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">–</emphasis>
9.4 mm
</quantity>
(N=4), width 
<quantity box="[759,894,1583,1607]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0999999999999996" metricValueMax="3.3" metricValueMin="2.9" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" unit="mm" value="3.0999999999999996" valueMax="3.3" valueMin="2.9">
2.9 
<emphasis box="[794,808,1584,1607]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">–</emphasis>
3.3 mm
</quantity>
(N=4), length/width = 2.87 
<emphasis box="[1206,1220,1584,1607]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">–</emphasis>
3.34 (N=4). Brown fumose, R-veins brown, posterior veins concolourous with membrane. 
<collectingRegion box="[998,1062,1619,1643]" country="New Zealand" name="West Coast" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Costa</collectingRegion>
